The paper presents a new large-scale knowledge graph in the academic domain, which includes information about papers, authors, fields of study, venues, and institutes. The paper also discusses data mining tasks such as link prediction, community detection, and scholar classification. These topics are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
